data.description: Welcome to 5057 Tin Top Rd. in Weatherford TX! This property offers a perfect blend of space, comfort and tranquility for your family's lifestyle. Tree lined for privacy, this corner lot boasts over 2500 sq ft of living space. Two large living spaces, provide ample room for relaxation and entertainment.  the large open kitchen is the perfect size for gathering with loved ones.  With five bedrooms and three bathrooms, there's plenty of space for everyone to have their privacy.  it ensures a comfortable and functional living space for all family members.  Located just four minutes away from the Brazos River public boat ramp, outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the convenience of accessing water activities and nature.  There are three storage buildings on the property and a back covered porch to relax and unwind.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this secluded corner lot yours!
